WEBVTT

01:38.160 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 3

01:45.200 --> 01:47.160
It's a personal vendetta.

01:47.240 --> 01:49.800
You should just keep moving.

01:49.880 --> 01:51.880
What kind of a vendetta requires torture?

01:51.960 --> 01:53.320
It's just a game.

01:55.320 --> 01:57.920
If you don't want to die,
make yourself scarce now.

02:02.520 --> 02:05.360
I'm back. I'll handle this.

02:07.280 --> 02:09.039
Hey! You've really crossed the line!

02:09.120 --> 02:11.400
Right, so what
if you're the number one player?

02:11.480 --> 02:13.480
You're way too rude to girls.

02:13.840 --> 02:15.440
It's just a game. Why get so worked up?

02:16.120 --> 02:17.880
Does being in a game
give you the right to be rude?

02:17.960 --> 02:20.040
Or give you the right
to bully those less skilled?

02:23.240 --> 02:25.080
Let's duke it out, as per custom.

02:25.920 --> 02:28.480
It's three of you against the two of us.
If you win, take the man and leave.

02:29.400 --> 02:31.440
We won't give him grief again.

02:34.280 --> 02:36.600
You go rest. I'll handle it.

02:38.320 --> 02:39.320
I'll watch.

02:42.480 --> 02:45.520
Can one of him defeat the three of us?

02:45.600 --> 02:49.080
I hear he's really good, though.
He's the number one player.

02:49.160 --> 02:51.480
Would he really hit girls? You think?

02:53.080 --> 02:56.400
Hey! What's going on? Who's duking it out?

02:56.480 --> 02:57.920
What? Lady!

02:58.000 --> 03:00.360
I took a shower,
and you're still hacking away?

03:01.040 --> 03:02.920
Shixie, it's me!

03:03.000 --> 03:05.080
Mianmian? What are you doing here?

03:05.520 --> 03:06.360
I've come to help.

03:07.640 --> 03:08.560
It's okay.

03:08.640 --> 03:11.640
There is bad blood between us.
It's good to get it resolved.

03:11.720 --> 03:14.200
Anyway, pretty girls are to be pampered.

03:14.280 --> 03:15.680
How can I let you fight for me?

03:15.760 --> 03:16.880
Hey.

03:18.240 --> 03:20.640
It doesn't pay to be a good guy.
Let's go, Mianmian.

03:22.960 --> 03:26.000
Lady, hurry up with the hacking already.

03:26.080 --> 03:28.720
I still have 200 blood points.

03:28.800 --> 03:31.120
I'll go do my laundry.
Will you be done by then?

03:33.840 --> 03:37.400
You've got a mean tongue,
but you're kind enough at heart.

03:42.520 --> 03:46.400
Fine. I don't want to waste money
on the internet and electricity.

03:46.480 --> 03:47.640
I'll go collect herbs.

03:48.320 --> 03:49.320
Let's go.

03:52.520 --> 03:55.280
Wait, can't you unbind the Swing Rope
before you go?

03:55.360 --> 03:56.200
Hey!

04:01.840 --> 04:05.560
How did you know Modao Shixie
was in a compulsion loop?

04:05.880 --> 04:07.720
I logged on this afternoon,

04:07.920 --> 04:11.200
and he said in the public chat room that
he needed many monster skill books.

04:11.280 --> 04:14.560
So I know Modao Shixie
is in a compulsion loop.

04:16.040 --> 04:19.440
Why would a compulsion loop require
collecting monster skill books?

04:19.519 --> 04:22.000
A variety of quests
also need monster skill books.

04:23.240 --> 04:25.320
NPC quest givers are all different.

04:25.400 --> 04:29.000
A compulsion loop requires collecting
monster skill books at Level 236

04:29.360 --> 04:31.480
where the NPC is Wu Nandai.

04:32.080 --> 04:35.120
I waited there for a while,
and he soon showed up.

04:36.600 --> 04:42.240
You remember the level
and the NPC at that level?

04:42.880 --> 04:44.720
Your memory is incredible!

04:48.280 --> 04:51.920
By the way, you said you saw Modao Shixie
in the afternoon.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.000
Why didn't you take him out then?

04:56.240 --> 04:58.600
He was only at Level 205.

04:58.760 --> 05:01.680
I waited until he got to Level 299,
the last Level.

05:01.880 --> 05:06.160
Isn't it more impactful
for him to fail at the very last step?

05:07.480 --> 05:10.000
Yes, you win.

05:19.360 --> 05:21.400
Thank you, Naihe.

05:25.720 --> 05:28.720
Don't thank me. It was my duty.

05:31.040 --> 05:31.880
Not for that.

05:35.840 --> 05:37.200
This afternoon,

05:37.440 --> 05:40.800
I was rather upset over something.

05:41.360 --> 05:45.000
I didn't show it.
I didn't want my roommates to worry.

05:45.920 --> 05:49.200
But now, I'm all of a sudden really happy.

05:50.440 --> 05:51.280
Because of me?

05:56.120 --> 05:56.960
Because of you.

06:00.720 --> 06:01.560
That's good.

06:06.040 --> 06:08.480
Yaoyao, look over there. It's so pretty.

06:12.280 --> 06:13.920
- Yaoyao!
- Yaoyao!

06:14.000 --> 06:15.520
That hag, Luwei Weiwei, bullied us again!

06:15.960 --> 06:17.120
- Yes!
- It's true!

06:17.720 --> 06:20.640
Didn't I tell you to stay away from her?
Don't mind her.

06:21.240 --> 06:24.480
We're about to join their Bihai Clan.
We can't be on bad terms.

06:25.760 --> 06:27.520
We couldn't stand by
and watch her bully others.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.440
You guys!

06:32.360 --> 06:33.200
I have an idea!

06:34.080 --> 06:36.040
The official site
announced a video contest.

06:36.200 --> 06:39.160
Why don't we make a video
and get on their nerves?

06:41.880 --> 06:43.600
What video contest?

06:43.680 --> 06:45.720
It's using the game's
video recording function

06:45.800 --> 06:47.960
and make a love story
with the "A Chinese Ghost Story" theme.

06:48.040 --> 06:49.680
The topic is "Our Story."

06:49.760 --> 06:52.360
Like a micro film, it can be any length.

06:52.440 --> 06:55.600
The players will vote for a winner,
and the prize is great.

06:55.680 --> 06:58.320
The winner will get
a seven-colored in-game couple's outfit.

06:58.400 --> 07:00.080
Okay! Let's make a video.

07:00.160 --> 07:02.800
We'll win,
and Luwei Weiwei will eat her heart out!

07:04.080 --> 07:06.840
I don't think that's necessary.
Why publicize it to everyone?

07:08.640 --> 07:11.120
The seven-colored outfit may be pretty,

07:11.280 --> 07:13.840
but if Zhenshui is against it,
then never mind.

07:14.680 --> 07:16.840
Yaoyao, you're the bigger person,

07:16.920 --> 07:18.720
and shopping is always more fun.

07:18.800 --> 07:20.680
We'll shop for more nice outfits.

07:20.760 --> 07:22.560
- Sure.
- I should log off.

07:22.640 --> 07:24.680
I'm meeting a cousin for dinner.
I'll be back.

07:24.760 --> 07:26.080
- I'll be waiting.
- Okay.

07:44.280 --> 07:46.520
The laptop is fixed. Check it out.

07:47.760 --> 07:51.040
- Where are you going, Yiran?
- To the restroom.

07:54.440 --> 07:58.160
Thank you. Um, can I ask you something?

07:58.240 --> 07:59.400
Go ahead.

07:59.480 --> 08:03.120
- Did Xiao Nai know that we needed help?
- Yes.

08:03.200 --> 08:06.880
- Did he know that it's Yiran's laptop?
- Yes.

08:07.120 --> 08:09.040
Then why didn't he come?

08:09.120 --> 08:10.600
How should I know?

08:11.160 --> 08:13.400
Well, the laptop's fixed. I should go.

08:13.880 --> 08:17.360
Hey, don't be mad! Have a drink.

08:18.640 --> 08:21.720
Don't be mad.
I'm only anxious for Yiran's sake.

08:22.000 --> 08:27.120
Anyway, thank you for fixing her laptop.
I'll treat you to a meal next time.

08:28.520 --> 08:31.760
That's okay. Thanks for the drink.

08:38.520 --> 08:39.640
Yiran?

08:39.720 --> 08:42.840
Leave me alone.
Your terrible idea backfired.

08:42.960 --> 08:46.440
Now he knows for sure. I'm so embarrassed.

08:46.720 --> 08:48.160
My mom was right.

08:48.240 --> 08:50.960
Girls shouldn't be so aggressive.
We should be demure.

08:54.040 --> 08:57.200
Don't be sad, Yiran.

08:57.400 --> 08:59.320
I asked Yu just now.

08:59.400 --> 09:02.120
Xiao Nai had to be somewhere else
at the last minute.

09:02.400 --> 09:04.680
He's upset he couldn't be here.

09:05.440 --> 09:08.560
We'll find another opportunity. Okay?

09:09.600 --> 09:10.760
Really?

09:11.720 --> 09:12.960
I promise.

09:24.280 --> 09:25.920
Hello, Cousin Shaoxiang?

09:26.720 --> 09:29.480
Little Yiran,
do you still want to go to dinner?

09:30.440 --> 09:32.480
Not today. I'm not in the mood.

09:32.760 --> 09:37.000
You should go, Yiran.
It's good to get a change of scenery.

09:37.080 --> 09:39.840
Maybe you can pick his brains, too?

09:41.760 --> 09:43.560
Fine. Then I want a feast tonight.

09:44.320 --> 09:47.160
Sure! It's always a feast
when you dine out with me.

09:47.240 --> 09:49.000
Let's meet at 6:30.

09:49.080 --> 09:50.720
Pick a place and let me know.

09:51.560 --> 09:52.880
All right. See you later.

09:56.520 --> 09:59.920
Mr. Shaoxiang, my friends told me
about this restaurant.

10:00.000 --> 10:01.840
I've been wanting to come.

10:03.560 --> 10:05.360
Thank you, Mr. Shaoxiang.

10:05.600 --> 10:06.560
You're welcome.

10:08.320 --> 10:09.400
- Here.
- Thanks.

10:14.320 --> 10:16.520
What's wrong? Why are you brooding?

10:17.640 --> 10:18.640
It's nothing.

10:21.120 --> 10:22.720
You should tell Mr. Shaoxiang.

10:25.680 --> 10:28.520
You have a secret? Let me guess.

10:29.480 --> 10:31.760
Boy trouble? Do tell.

10:41.160 --> 10:44.280
Yiran, you should talk to Mr. Shaoxiang.

10:44.360 --> 10:47.160
Maybe he can offer you advice.

10:49.320 --> 10:50.400
Then you tell me.

10:52.000 --> 10:56.400
Well, Yiran is fond of a boy
from our school's computer department.

10:56.480 --> 10:58.960
We asked him to come fix her laptop,

10:59.480 --> 11:02.120
but he was busy, so he didn't show up.

11:02.360 --> 11:04.360
Is he not into me at all?

11:05.440 --> 11:06.880
Is that why he didn't show up?

11:08.160 --> 11:11.480
My little cousin,
have more confidence in yourself.

11:11.960 --> 11:13.960
With your looks, personality,
and family background,

11:14.760 --> 11:16.960
no man in his right mind
would ever reject you.

11:17.680 --> 11:21.320
He's different. He's a genius.

11:21.600 --> 11:22.720
He's no average guy.

11:24.400 --> 11:27.720
He's rather quiet and aloof.

11:28.200 --> 11:30.920
- Smug, is he? What's his name?
- Xiao Nai.

11:31.320 --> 11:32.520
Xiao Nai?

11:34.720 --> 11:35.880
That seems to ring a bell.

11:40.120 --> 11:41.360
I remember now!

11:41.800 --> 11:44.400
He's the guy in charge
of that company, Zhiyi Tech!

11:45.400 --> 11:47.800
You know Xiao Nai, Cousin Shaoxiang?

11:48.400 --> 11:51.120
My dad has been thinking
about acquiring his company.

11:52.000 --> 11:54.200
Uncle is acquiring Xiao Nai's company?

11:54.960 --> 11:56.520
We've been in touch.

11:56.800 --> 11:59.040
My dad wants
to expand the online gaming business.

11:59.120 --> 12:00.840
So he picked Zhiyi Tech.

12:01.160 --> 12:03.360
College students' teams are cheap.

12:03.680 --> 12:06.000
How's the negotiation going?

12:06.600 --> 12:07.880
It's as good as done.

12:07.960 --> 12:11.520
College students' teams
are lucky to have acquisition offers.

12:11.600 --> 12:13.000
Why would they turn him down?

12:13.560 --> 12:16.040
Will Xiao Nai be working for Uncle then?

12:16.880 --> 12:18.960
Of course! Everyone on the team is ours.

12:21.000 --> 12:24.680
Yiran, you can be an intern
at your uncle's company.

12:24.760 --> 12:26.280
If the deal goes through,

12:26.360 --> 12:29.000
you'll be working with Xiao Nai. Right?

12:29.720 --> 12:31.680
That's right! Why didn't I think of it?

12:33.920 --> 12:39.040
Cousin Shaoxiang, will you ask Uncle
to make me an intern at his company?

12:40.160 --> 12:41.960
Why do you suddenly want an internship?

12:42.800 --> 12:45.160
I have plenty of time anyway.

12:45.400 --> 12:46.720
Ask Uncle for me.

12:46.800 --> 12:49.880
Any position will do. I can do anything.

12:50.040 --> 12:54.560
No, you want to be an assistant
with the game development division.

12:56.560 --> 12:58.600
Right, game development division.

12:59.880 --> 13:01.040
It's because of Xiao Nai?

13:02.480 --> 13:06.240
I'm curious. Who is this guy, Xiao Nai?

13:07.240 --> 13:10.080
Why would my super-picky cousin
be so fond of him?

13:11.800 --> 13:17.560
Cousin Shaoxiang,
please ask Uncle for me!

13:17.640 --> 13:20.560
Fine. I'm dizzy from all this shaking.

13:21.000 --> 13:23.320
I'll ask my dad for you,

13:23.400 --> 13:25.400
but don't blame me if it doesn't work out.

13:25.480 --> 13:27.560
I trust you can get it done.

13:29.520 --> 13:31.400
I think Huadun is nice.

13:31.480 --> 13:33.280
Lots of money and no interference.

13:33.520 --> 13:35.480
We already have a good R&D team,

13:35.560 --> 13:38.240
but we're lacking in distribution
and marketing channels.

13:38.320 --> 13:39.640
We have plenty of funds.

13:39.720 --> 13:42.680
We should pick one with distribution
and marketing resources.

13:43.120 --> 13:45.000
What about Fengteng and NetEase?

13:45.080 --> 13:46.720
Those two are good, too.

13:46.800 --> 13:49.640
Most importantly,
they offered us an olive branch.

13:50.760 --> 13:53.600
Zhenyi Tech is nice, too.
You have a meeting, right?

13:53.680 --> 13:55.920
Yes, their headquarters
is in Capital City.

13:56.000 --> 13:57.320
We're meeting the day after tomorrow.

13:57.400 --> 13:59.880
Next week, I'll visit
Fengteng's headquarters in Shanghai.

14:00.920 --> 14:03.880
All done with business?
I have gossip to share.

14:05.240 --> 14:07.920
This morning,
I went to fix Meng Yiran's laptop.

14:08.040 --> 14:12.040
When she didn't see Nai,
she didn't even bother to look at me.

14:12.120 --> 14:15.400
Yu, you knew this was coming, right?

14:16.160 --> 14:21.800
Mei, it felt so awful!
You're always so good to me!

14:23.640 --> 14:27.280
Get lost! You don't get to shake me!

14:27.560 --> 14:29.760
All done with business. I should go.

14:29.840 --> 14:31.680
You're not staying at the dorm, again?

14:33.080 --> 14:35.320
When you guys wash your dirty socks,

14:35.520 --> 14:36.680
I'll come back.

14:37.720 --> 14:39.440
- Bye-bye.
- Bye.

14:42.000 --> 14:45.520
I don't care, you have to visit me
in Capital City during the summer.

14:50.440 --> 14:54.160
Breaking news:
Pecans and macadamia nuts are on sale.

14:54.240 --> 14:55.560
Do you want any?

14:55.640 --> 14:58.040
- I want two bags of macadamia nuts.
- Okay!

15:00.720 --> 15:02.760
We got interview invitations!

15:02.840 --> 15:06.600
- Erxi, why are you screaming nonstop?
- What interview?

15:06.880 --> 15:09.040
Zhenyi Tech's summer internship.

15:09.120 --> 15:12.320
I applied for all of us.
We got to the interview round.

15:12.640 --> 15:14.840
- They replied already?
- I'll call you back.

15:15.440 --> 15:17.480
Big corporations are great, efficient.

15:17.720 --> 15:19.880
All of us got through to the interview.

15:19.960 --> 15:21.000
Very wise of them.

15:22.240 --> 15:24.360
The interview is the day after tomorrow.

15:24.440 --> 15:26.040
Thursday. We don't have classes.

15:27.080 --> 15:29.800
The interview will be held
at Zhenyi Tech's conference room.

15:31.000 --> 15:34.560
Should we maybe dress up
like office ladies?

15:35.200 --> 15:38.120
Are you kidding? We're students.

15:38.200 --> 15:40.920
We have to look
like vivacious college kids.

15:41.320 --> 15:44.360
Plus, they want interns
for the game development division.

15:44.680 --> 15:48.360
We must dress like geeky girls.

15:56.840 --> 16:01.520
Right. This is settled, then. Okay?

16:02.920 --> 16:04.800
- Great.
- Uncle!

16:05.960 --> 16:08.240
Yiran? What are you doing here?

16:08.320 --> 16:11.280
Why? Aren't you happy to see me?

16:11.680 --> 16:13.200
Yes, very happy!

16:14.120 --> 16:15.560
No class today?

16:15.880 --> 16:18.320
Dad, Yiran is very mature now.

16:18.640 --> 16:20.320
She's hard-working at school,

16:20.520 --> 16:23.760
and she's been asking me
to find her an internship.

16:23.840 --> 16:26.520
Then I thought,
aren't we looking for interns?

16:26.600 --> 16:27.880
So, here she is.

16:28.600 --> 16:31.040
Uncle, please let me be an intern here.

16:31.120 --> 16:34.240
So I can be here every day
and give you a shoulder rub.

16:35.600 --> 16:37.320
You're welcome to come,

16:37.520 --> 16:39.280
but I worry
it'd distract from your studies.

16:39.360 --> 16:42.520
If that happened,
your parents would chew me out.

16:42.600 --> 16:47.480
Don't worry, Uncle. I promise,
I'll manage both school and internship.

16:50.400 --> 16:53.400
I watched you grow up, you know?

16:53.480 --> 16:55.440
You've always been like a daughter to me.

16:55.920 --> 16:59.000
Have I ever said no to you?

16:59.520 --> 17:00.760
Thanks, Uncle!

17:02.760 --> 17:05.480
Well, then. You can start as my assistant.

17:05.920 --> 17:08.240
I'll show you around the office later.

17:08.400 --> 17:11.240
Sure. I'll do as you say, Uncle.

17:11.960 --> 17:16.319
Mr. Zhen, the CEO of Zhiyi Tech,
Mr. Xiao is here.

17:17.480 --> 17:21.720
Have him come up. Have Mr. Lee
from investment division join us.

17:22.160 --> 17:23.000
Got it.

17:24.400 --> 17:27.160
Son, show her around the office.

17:27.240 --> 17:29.480
- Help her get to know the place.
- Sure.

17:29.760 --> 17:32.480
I'm not leaving, Uncle.
I want to start the internship now.

17:33.960 --> 17:35.760
I'll be in a business meeting.

17:35.840 --> 17:37.360
I won't bother you.

17:37.760 --> 17:40.360
I'll serve you tea.

17:40.440 --> 17:42.600
Please, Uncle?

17:43.360 --> 17:44.960
Fine.

17:45.040 --> 17:47.000
- I'll go get ready.
- Okay.

17:47.080 --> 17:48.400
I'll stay, too.

17:48.480 --> 17:51.080
I'd like to see...

17:58.640 --> 17:59.880
What is it?

17:59.960 --> 18:02.040
Don't go back there, please.

18:02.120 --> 18:05.640
It's weird with so many others there.
I'll be fine on my own.

18:06.600 --> 18:10.800
Please! Go take a stroll.
I'll treat you to a meal.

18:10.880 --> 18:12.080
Promise?

18:12.840 --> 18:14.920
By the way, do I look pretty today?

18:15.200 --> 18:16.440
Yes.

18:19.360 --> 18:21.000
Can I use those mugs?

18:21.080 --> 18:22.680
Sure. Help yourself.

18:31.560 --> 18:35.440
This way, please. Mr. Li is here.

18:35.560 --> 18:36.560
Hello, Mr. Xiao.

18:36.640 --> 18:37.680
- Hi.
- Nice to see you again.

18:37.760 --> 18:38.600
- Mr. Yu.
- Hi.

18:38.680 --> 18:40.040
This way, please.

18:44.080 --> 18:45.360
This way.

18:46.520 --> 18:47.560
Mr. Zhen?

18:47.920 --> 18:49.400
- Welcome!
- Mr. Zhen.

18:49.960 --> 18:53.400
- Mr. Xiao, you're so young!
- Hello.

18:53.480 --> 18:56.800
Young and capable! Come, have a seat.

18:59.440 --> 19:00.360
Please sit.

19:09.040 --> 19:10.080
Yiran?

19:19.400 --> 19:22.080
I got a briefing
from our investment division.

19:22.400 --> 19:24.880
I'm very interested in your work.

19:26.000 --> 19:28.400
Yes, Mr. Zhen thinks highly of you.

19:28.480 --> 19:30.320
He wanted to meet as soon as possible.

19:31.360 --> 19:32.200
Thanks, Mr. Zhen.

19:32.520 --> 19:33.800
Have some tea.

19:53.120 --> 19:55.200
Next up, Li Xiaofeng.

19:56.240 --> 19:57.840
Okay. Thanks.

19:59.080 --> 20:00.520
Hold on a second.

20:03.360 --> 20:05.160
- Thanks.
- Please wait here.

20:08.000 --> 20:10.200
How come there are so many people?

20:11.080 --> 20:13.640
It's a big company.
Everyone wants to get in.

20:18.200 --> 20:21.360
Stinky Xiaoling! Stinky Sisi!
They refuse to sit with me!

20:21.440 --> 20:24.160
They must be worried
that I'd outshine them.

20:25.560 --> 20:28.360
Erxi, it's good to be confident,

20:28.480 --> 20:30.880
but it should be based on reality.

20:30.960 --> 20:33.560
- Et tu, Brute?
- Stop it.

20:34.000 --> 20:36.520
Wait here. I'll go snoop around for info.

20:44.160 --> 20:45.000
Two waters, please.

20:45.080 --> 20:47.000
- Sure.
- Thanks.

20:49.760 --> 20:50.760
Thanks.

21:06.960 --> 21:08.200
Next!

21:10.360 --> 21:12.200
Hey! Can I ask you something?

21:12.280 --> 21:14.480
What questions did they ask you?

21:14.560 --> 21:16.480
Like, have you played any games?

21:16.560 --> 21:18.600
They also asked about your avatar handle.

21:18.680 --> 21:21.240
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

21:32.120 --> 21:33.280
Well?

21:37.040 --> 21:38.400
The rest is nothing,

21:38.480 --> 21:40.840
but since we want
to get into game development,

21:40.920 --> 21:46.320
they'll ask us if we've played any games

21:46.680 --> 21:48.560
and our avatar handles.

21:48.640 --> 21:49.640
What now, Weiwei?

21:49.800 --> 21:51.640
Besides you, none of us has ever played.

21:53.240 --> 21:55.440
- Go get Xiaoling and Sisi.
- Okay!

22:07.840 --> 22:11.200
Our company
wasn't always in the gaming industry.

22:11.280 --> 22:14.280
It's because my son is really into gaming,

22:14.680 --> 22:17.200
and he'd blow a bunch of money on games.

22:17.280 --> 22:19.760
That's how I saw the potential in gaming.

22:19.840 --> 22:24.240
We decided to develop a game,
and it turned out to be very popular.

22:25.200 --> 22:27.520
Our company successfully transitioned

22:27.680 --> 22:30.280
as I happened to catch the industry trend.

22:31.680 --> 22:33.760
RX is a good game indeed.

22:33.920 --> 22:36.680
That was a historical decision.

22:36.760 --> 22:38.800
Mr. Zhen is a visionary.

22:40.880 --> 22:45.400
Real success
relies on having great products.

22:45.760 --> 22:49.360
We've given it a lot of thought,
and we're so hungry for talent.

22:50.080 --> 22:52.720
When Mr. Li recommended your game,

22:53.200 --> 22:55.600
I knew right away
that there's something in it.

22:58.320 --> 23:00.120
We're all technical people.

23:00.200 --> 23:03.840
Instead of beating around the bush,
I'll get to the point.

23:04.000 --> 23:08.200
We'd like to buy the rights to your game
for three million,

23:08.280 --> 23:12.120
and we'd like you to come work for us
to finish the development.

23:12.200 --> 23:14.480
We'll pay a lucrative salary, of course.

23:16.160 --> 23:17.160
Well...

23:21.480 --> 23:25.480
The thing is, we're also developing games
with similar ideas.

23:25.920 --> 23:28.560
If Mr. Xiao would direct the projects,

23:28.640 --> 23:31.000
we'll be more confident with the result.

23:32.000 --> 23:35.120
We will surely give a lot of thought
to the gracious offer.

23:36.440 --> 23:38.200
We're very sincere.

23:38.720 --> 23:42.400
Our company needs new blood like you guys.

23:42.760 --> 23:47.560
That's right. Mr. Zhen is a rarity.
Nowadays, not many would be willing

23:47.640 --> 23:48.760
to invest in college students.

23:49.200 --> 23:51.840
Mr. Xiao, don't pass up the opportunity.

23:53.000 --> 23:53.840
Right.

23:55.280 --> 23:57.960
Good, I'll wait to hear back from you.

23:58.840 --> 24:03.040
- Mr. Xiao, you go to Qing University?
- Yes.

24:03.400 --> 24:07.080
What a coincidence!
My niece is also a student there.

24:07.160 --> 24:10.040
I hear she's quite famous on campus.

24:10.440 --> 24:14.360
- Do you know each other?
- I'm sorry. I don't think we've met.

24:16.600 --> 24:20.840
You must be wholly devoted
to your studies and career.

24:21.280 --> 24:25.160
It's fine.
Young people get to know each other fast.

24:25.240 --> 24:26.520
We'll see.

24:28.520 --> 24:31.200
Mr. Zhen, Mr. Li,
we won't take up more of your time.

24:31.440 --> 24:33.560
Okay. I have a meeting, too.

24:34.720 --> 24:39.040
- Xiaowang, see them out.
- Sure. This way, please.

24:49.480 --> 24:53.400
- We'll see ourselves out.
- Okay. Thank you. Goodbye.

25:00.120 --> 25:01.720
What do they take us for?

25:01.800 --> 25:03.480
They want our life's work
with that crappy offer?

25:03.560 --> 25:06.240
That's a joke!
They think we're that gullible?

25:06.320 --> 25:07.480
And you thought about it!

25:07.560 --> 25:09.920
Why? What's there to consider?

25:10.000 --> 25:13.200
- I was acting.
- You were acting?

25:15.840 --> 25:17.520
What the heck?

25:17.600 --> 25:20.520
Why? Just reject them outright!

25:21.480 --> 25:24.200
And that guy, Li something...

25:24.280 --> 25:27.560
Did he mean that deal or no deal,
he can use our idea anyway?

25:27.640 --> 25:29.480
- I didn't misunderstand?
- No.

25:29.960 --> 25:33.280
That's like hostile acquisition!
What do we do?

25:33.960 --> 25:36.080
They're using irregular tactics.

25:36.240 --> 25:38.720
So can we. Don't worry.

25:40.560 --> 25:42.840
You're summoning your Machiavellian side.

25:42.920 --> 25:44.440
Now I'm worried for them.

25:46.320 --> 25:49.680
You're too kind,
but we need to pick up the pace.

25:54.320 --> 25:56.040
Wait, Xiao Nai!

25:57.600 --> 26:00.720
Did Mr. Zhen want something, Ms. Meng?

26:01.000 --> 26:03.720
It's not Mr. Zhen. It's me.

26:06.560 --> 26:09.280
Go ahead. I'll go to the bathroom.

26:10.120 --> 26:11.120
Xiao Nai...

26:11.520 --> 26:16.160
Xiao Nai, my uncle's ideas
can be too old-fashioned.

26:16.240 --> 26:19.960
If he's said anything upsetting,
please don't be mad.

26:20.520 --> 26:23.560
Don't say that, Ms. Meng.
It's just a business meeting.

26:24.600 --> 26:30.360
Maybe I can help you convince my uncle
and get you a better deal?

26:30.880 --> 26:31.880
That's okay.

26:32.080 --> 26:35.680
It may not be appropriate to do that,
given your position.

26:36.120 --> 26:38.680
Thanks a lot, though. I should go.

26:40.560 --> 26:41.760
I'll meet you downstairs.

26:43.720 --> 26:45.840
That's the guy who's stolen your heart?

26:46.080 --> 26:48.800
Poor and backward,
yet arrogant to the max!

26:48.960 --> 26:50.720
Your parents would never accept him.

26:50.800 --> 26:54.800
I don't care.
If I like him, my parents will accept him.

26:54.920 --> 26:58.960
Plus, he's great. The more he is himself,
the more I like him.

26:59.480 --> 27:04.320
Cousin Shaoxiang, help me convince Uncle
to work with Xiao Nai!

27:05.400 --> 27:08.520
Little cousin--
No, I'll call you Lady Meng, okay?

27:08.600 --> 27:12.480
Please, it's my dad's company.
I don't call the shots.

27:15.000 --> 27:17.200
Then I'll convince Uncle myself.

27:19.280 --> 27:21.080
- Got it?
- Yes.

27:21.160 --> 27:24.400
If they ask about the game,
it's "A Chinese Ghost Story."

27:24.480 --> 27:28.280
The server is Capital City Bests.
My handle is Luwei Yipian.

27:28.600 --> 27:30.800
My handle is Yipian Luwei.

27:30.880 --> 27:33.680
Mine is Luwei Luwei.

27:33.760 --> 27:36.600
Weiwei, what's with you and Luwei?

27:36.800 --> 27:38.200
They're all my subaccounts.

27:38.280 --> 27:40.320
Use my subaccounts for the interview.

27:40.480 --> 27:42.920
Tell them we're all roommates.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.760
It's normal to have similar names.

27:44.840 --> 27:48.720
If necessary, I can give you guys
extra training afterward.

27:48.800 --> 27:50.800
Fine. Got it.

27:50.880 --> 27:54.040
It's not rocket science, okay?

27:54.840 --> 27:55.880
Show some appreciation!

27:55.960 --> 27:58.680
Sorry. Please forgive me!

27:59.720 --> 28:02.760
- Next up, Zhao Erxi.
- Here!

28:03.240 --> 28:05.880
Weiwei, will you come with me?

28:06.560 --> 28:08.960
- You're too easily rattled. Go.
- Come on!

28:10.600 --> 28:12.680
- Bye-bye.
- Break a leg!

28:15.560 --> 28:18.880
- Hi, I'm Zhao Erxi.
- Please wait over there.

28:20.200 --> 28:21.080
Let's go.

28:22.600 --> 28:23.440
Sit.

28:25.680 --> 28:27.360
Mr. Zhen, it's for you.

28:28.920 --> 28:30.560
- It's fine.
- Who's this?

28:30.720 --> 28:34.080
Mr. Feng? I'm free.
Let's talk in my office.

28:34.160 --> 28:35.600
Okay, then.

28:38.040 --> 28:38.880
Next!

28:39.200 --> 28:40.160
What?

28:41.720 --> 28:45.280
Cousin Shaoxiang,
why don't we go sit in on the interview?

28:45.360 --> 28:46.360
Whatever for?

28:46.800 --> 28:48.720
I'm curious.

28:48.800 --> 28:51.640
Know your enemy and yourself,
you shall win a hundred battles.

28:51.720 --> 28:55.640
At least I can prove to Uncle
that hiring me is a wise decision.

28:56.160 --> 28:58.360
It's just for a little while.

28:58.440 --> 29:00.480
I won't take up too much time.

29:01.720 --> 29:02.560
I promise.

29:03.480 --> 29:06.280
Fine, just for a little while. Let's go.

29:06.960 --> 29:09.560
- That's all for now.
- Thanks.

29:13.320 --> 29:14.400
Mr. Zhen.

29:14.480 --> 29:16.120
Don't mind me. Carry on.

29:18.800 --> 29:20.000
Next!

29:23.760 --> 29:24.800
Hello!

29:29.280 --> 29:30.200
Have a seat.

29:34.960 --> 29:37.240
- Are you Zhao Erxi?
- Yes.

29:37.960 --> 29:40.720
We already have
your background information.

29:40.960 --> 29:45.280
Please tell us about why you want
an internship with our company.

29:45.840 --> 29:50.600
Because I want to improve myself
through real workplace experiences,

29:51.360 --> 29:55.720
apply my learned knowledge
in development and innovation.

29:56.480 --> 29:58.640
Your company started out
as a cellphone manufacturer,

29:58.720 --> 30:01.440
yet you successfully transitioned
in a few short years.

30:01.520 --> 30:05.360
That proves you are a creative
and vivacious company.

30:05.440 --> 30:07.040
That's why I want to join you.

30:08.640 --> 30:10.080
Any other questions?

30:11.280 --> 30:13.080
You mentioned the gaming industry.

30:13.360 --> 30:15.560
Are you interested in game development?

30:15.640 --> 30:17.560
- I am!
- Good.

30:18.600 --> 30:21.320
Can you tell us
about your experiences with gaming?

30:21.400 --> 30:24.200
Which game or games
are you currently playing?

30:24.280 --> 30:27.640
I've been playing
"A Chinese Ghost Story Online Game."

30:28.040 --> 30:31.840
My character is a swordswoman in red,
called Luwei...

30:37.280 --> 30:39.720
- Luwei Weiwei!
- Luwei Weiwei?

30:42.960 --> 30:45.680
Yes? What is it?

30:46.040 --> 30:47.040
Which server are you on?

30:48.560 --> 30:49.920
Capital City Bests.

30:51.880 --> 30:53.400
Do you know me?

31:01.360 --> 31:06.160
Oh, no. Did I blow my cover?

31:06.240 --> 31:08.760
Is he Weiwei's friend from the game?

31:08.840 --> 31:10.080
Darn it!

31:10.160 --> 31:14.120
How come I got nervous
and totally forgot the subaccount handle?

31:14.200 --> 31:16.880
I should've just made one up.

31:16.960 --> 31:18.920
I'm doomed.

31:20.760 --> 31:23.600
What is it, Cousin Shaoxiang?

31:40.360 --> 31:43.040
You're all good. Wait for our news.

31:44.320 --> 31:45.600
Thanks.

31:48.880 --> 31:50.240
Next!

31:53.360 --> 31:57.280
What's wrong, Erxi? How did it go?

31:57.800 --> 32:01.800
It went pretty well,
except I made a little mistake.

32:02.160 --> 32:04.360
A little tiny one.

32:04.440 --> 32:05.680
This doesn't bode well.

32:08.280 --> 32:12.080
I forgot the subaccount you gave me.

32:12.160 --> 32:15.320
I was so nervous that I blurted out
your master account, Luwei Weiwei.

32:16.520 --> 32:19.760
That's no big deal.
I'll give them my subaccount.

32:20.440 --> 32:22.080
Thanks, Lady Weiwei!

32:22.320 --> 32:25.240
Also, I saw a guy in there
who seemed really odd.

32:25.800 --> 32:27.440
He was with Meng Yiran, too.

32:28.400 --> 32:30.200
He's so good-looking!

32:32.400 --> 32:35.080
But he seemed angry
when he heard the name Luwei Weiwei.

32:35.160 --> 32:37.000
Could he be your enemy in the game?

32:39.080 --> 32:42.040
I don't know. Who cares?
I'm just glad you didn't blow your cover.

32:44.480 --> 32:47.400
- My turn's coming soon. Wait for me.
- Okay.

33:04.840 --> 33:08.360
Nai, their office is huge.

33:08.680 --> 33:10.200
I almost got lost.

33:10.280 --> 33:12.680
I had to stand in line
to use the men's bathroom.

33:12.760 --> 33:14.080
- Break a leg!
- That means

33:14.160 --> 33:18.160
they have way more men than women here.

33:18.440 --> 33:19.960
- Let's go.
- Wait.

33:22.360 --> 33:24.880
What did the campus belle say to you?

33:25.280 --> 33:26.520
Did she confess her love?

33:29.120 --> 33:31.920
If you used your imagination
on game design,

33:32.000 --> 33:34.400
- I'd be more pleased.
- Whatever! Drop the act.

33:34.480 --> 33:36.080
She's been so obvious!

33:38.440 --> 33:39.280
Did you say yes?

33:48.280 --> 33:54.320
What a lucky day! First the campus belle,
now the department belle!

33:56.040 --> 33:56.880
Department belle?

33:57.440 --> 34:01.880
That's right. The one in the ponytail.
Her name is Bei Weiwei.

34:02.120 --> 34:04.000
Last year, we had a campus belle contest.

34:04.400 --> 34:07.520
She did well for our computer department.

34:08.000 --> 34:11.239
It proved once and for all,
computer department has pretty girls, too.

34:12.880 --> 34:17.159
Although the result wasn't ideal
and she only got second place.

34:17.239 --> 34:19.800
No campus belle title,
but department belle is good, too.

34:24.080 --> 34:26.880
What are you smiling at?

34:28.400 --> 34:31.719
Bei Weiwei? The name fits her.

34:33.920 --> 34:35.960
I should buy a lottery ticket today.

34:38.600 --> 34:41.880
First, I'm lucky enough
to see two gorgeous girls in one day,

34:42.199 --> 34:44.920
then I heard you
utter a girl's name out loud.

34:45.600 --> 34:47.199
My life is complete.

34:57.680 --> 35:01.120
Department belle is good.
Over the top is superfluous.

35:02.240 --> 35:04.200
What does that mean?

35:08.240 --> 35:10.200
Now, we wait for the notice.

35:10.280 --> 35:14.000
We've got real skills.
I'm sure we'll be fine.

35:14.920 --> 35:17.520
If the interviewers
don't know you're our roommate,

35:17.600 --> 35:20.120
we'll have a better chance.

35:20.200 --> 35:22.960
Come here, Xiaoling.
I promise I won't beat you up.

35:25.080 --> 35:27.000
- Come here!
- Stop it!

35:27.080 --> 35:29.240
Stop, you're too old for this.

35:29.440 --> 35:30.520
What time is it?

35:34.680 --> 35:37.040
I nearly forgot! I have tutoring today.

35:37.120 --> 35:39.560
- I won't go back to the dorm then.
- When will you be done?

35:40.760 --> 35:44.560
Today's a bit complicated.
Probably around eight or nine.

35:44.720 --> 35:46.240
Have dinner without me. See you.

35:46.320 --> 35:47.920
Bye-bye.

35:48.400 --> 35:51.040
- Come here, you!
- Stop it.

35:59.640 --> 36:00.640
Cao Guang!

36:02.480 --> 36:04.160
You showed up!

36:05.120 --> 36:07.760
I invited you. I wouldn't stand you up.

36:07.840 --> 36:09.400
Come on, I'll take you in.

36:21.600 --> 36:22.920
Is no one home?

36:28.960 --> 36:30.400
Welcome!

36:42.520 --> 36:44.560
What are you doing?

36:45.960 --> 36:49.280
- Ms. Weiwei, welcome!
- Thanks.

36:54.440 --> 36:56.400
Is Auntie out? Are you home alone?

36:56.680 --> 36:58.040
She went out.

37:01.480 --> 37:04.240
You're the English tutor
Ms. Weiwei mentioned?

37:04.720 --> 37:05.800
Yes.

37:08.520 --> 37:10.440
You don't look much.

37:17.280 --> 37:19.360
You're not going to get mad with a kid?

37:20.280 --> 37:21.640
I'm not that childish.

37:31.400 --> 37:33.680
Ms. Weiwei, look at this level!

37:33.760 --> 37:35.840
The game designer is mean!

37:37.080 --> 37:39.080
Wait, let me introduce you.

37:39.160 --> 37:42.080
This is Cao Guang, a rare talent
from the Foreign Languages Department.

37:42.160 --> 37:45.480
Aren't you looking for an English tutor?
You can give him a shot.

37:45.960 --> 37:47.920
This is Xiaoyang, my student.

37:49.480 --> 37:50.400
Hello, kid.

37:51.320 --> 37:52.640
I'm not a kid.

37:53.120 --> 37:55.080
Didn't you hear
how she called me Xiaoyang?

37:55.960 --> 37:57.200
I'm 12 years old.

37:57.360 --> 37:59.320
That's two-thirds of an adult.

38:02.120 --> 38:04.520
Ms. Weiwei, forget him.

38:04.600 --> 38:06.360
Show me how to pass this level.

38:06.440 --> 38:08.280
I'll check your homework first.

38:08.360 --> 38:10.400
How did it go
with the exercises I gave you last time?

38:10.480 --> 38:12.560
It was a piece of cake.

38:12.640 --> 38:14.680
I finished it in a day.

38:15.240 --> 38:17.960
- Amazing!
- You can check, if you want.

38:23.720 --> 38:24.920
Let me check it.

38:35.320 --> 38:38.560
Ms. Weiwei, I'm thirsty.
I want some coke.

38:39.920 --> 38:42.720
Coke is bad for you.
I'll see if there's juice.

38:44.280 --> 38:45.280
Thank you.

38:46.480 --> 38:49.760
Wait here. He'll keep you company.

38:50.040 --> 38:50.880
Me?

39:29.480 --> 39:31.560
Has Bei Weiwei been your tutor for long?

39:32.800 --> 39:37.840
Yes, Ms. Weiwei is exceptionally smart.
That's why she can teach me.

39:39.040 --> 39:42.800
You don't look so smart.
Let's just forget it.

39:48.800 --> 39:52.200
Is the way she knocked on the door
a code between you two?

39:54.000 --> 39:55.200
You know Morse code?

39:56.000 --> 39:59.320
Of course I know of Morse code,
but in terms of reading...

40:00.520 --> 40:03.840
- You can't read Morse code?
- No.

40:04.760 --> 40:05.640
That's to be expected.

40:05.840 --> 40:09.360
A simple language
that can convey all communication

40:09.560 --> 40:11.040
isn't for the average folk.

40:12.840 --> 40:16.400
You mean she was talking to you?

40:17.160 --> 40:18.600
It's a coded message.

40:19.360 --> 40:22.160
Sometimes, I'm home all by myself.

40:22.240 --> 40:24.520
Ms. Weiwei taught me Morse code.

40:24.600 --> 40:26.560
I'm not to open the door to door bells.

40:27.000 --> 40:29.000
I only open the door to Morse code.

40:30.920 --> 40:32.600
Interesting.

40:33.960 --> 40:35.520
What did her coded message say?

40:36.360 --> 40:39.680
I'm not telling you.
It's a secret between me and Ms. Weiwei.

40:41.160 --> 40:44.280
Fine, secret.

40:46.560 --> 40:47.760
Here, have some juice.

40:47.840 --> 40:52.240
Ms. Weiwei, this guy said
he's too busy to tutor me.

40:53.200 --> 40:56.880
- When did I--
- Plus, I don't want to learn English.

40:57.840 --> 41:01.160
Xiaoyang, in order to become
a great programmer,

41:01.240 --> 41:03.040
you must excel in English.

41:03.800 --> 41:06.120
Can't you teach me English?

41:07.120 --> 41:09.440
My English isn't good enough.

41:10.440 --> 41:15.120
But if you don't like this tutor,

41:15.200 --> 41:18.040
- we can find you another one.
- Okay.

41:27.320 --> 41:29.840
Kid, I'll come see you again soon.

41:33.000 --> 41:36.480
Work on your homework.
I made it much harder this time.

41:36.640 --> 41:37.760
See you.

41:38.320 --> 41:39.720
Ms. Weiwei!

41:44.240 --> 41:45.280
What is it?

41:45.520 --> 41:50.160
Ms. Weiwei, is that guy your boyfriend?

41:51.960 --> 41:54.520
What's going on
in that little head of yours?

41:54.600 --> 41:57.520
- He's just my fellow student.
- Good to know.

41:57.640 --> 42:00.600
I checked him out for you. He's no good.

42:05.000 --> 42:06.120
I see.

42:06.200 --> 42:09.160
If he wants to court me,
I'll be sure to turn him down.

42:09.240 --> 42:10.760
That's it.

42:11.480 --> 42:15.720
But you're getting on in age.
You should fall in love.

42:16.520 --> 42:19.040
I picked one for you. See if you like him.

42:28.280 --> 42:29.440
Well? What do you think?

42:29.520 --> 42:31.240
Is he perfect or what?

42:31.520 --> 42:33.960
He goes to the same school as you.

42:36.280 --> 42:37.960
You've got great taste.

42:38.680 --> 42:42.360
But he's the most popular guy on campus.
He's out of my league.

42:43.960 --> 42:45.640
Ms. Weiwei, you're a catch, too.

42:45.720 --> 42:47.440
I believe in you. Good luck!

42:49.760 --> 42:50.840
By the way, Ms. Weiwei,

42:50.920 --> 42:54.400
will you bring your gaming notebook
next time for me to study?

42:55.720 --> 42:58.120
Sure. Finish your homework first.

42:58.480 --> 43:00.680
- See you!
- Bye-bye.

43:00.760 --> 43:01.920
Bye-bye.

43:05.680 --> 43:08.160
Xiaoyang's mom will be home
in 10 minutes.

43:08.240 --> 43:11.560
- Let's say hi before we go.
- Say hi to his mom? Why?

43:12.920 --> 43:15.040
Didn't you want to see his mom's car?

43:15.120 --> 43:17.600
Otherwise you'll accuse me
of faking the photo.

43:17.680 --> 43:19.200
It's okay.

